        "Npc4": [
            {
                "text": "Hello, What do you want to know?",
                "order": 1,
                "isOption": true,
                "Option_One_Text": "询问有关聚会当天的细节。",
                "Option_One_nextOrder": 2,
                "Option_Two_Text":"询问女管家个人的事情。",
                "Option_Two_nextOrder": 3
            },
            {
                "text": "",
                "order": 2,
                "isOption": true,
                "Option_One_Text": "询问女管家是否注意到了什么不寻常的事情。",
                "Option_One_nextOrder": 4,
                "Option_Two_Text":"询问女管家当天负责的工作内容。",
                "Option_Two_nextOrder": 5            },
            {
                "text": "",
                "order": 3,
                "isOption": true,
                "Option_One_Text": "直接质疑女管家是否参与了谋杀.",
                "Option_One_nextOrder": 6,
                "Option_Two_Text":"对女管家进行无关紧要的闲聊。",
                "Option_Two_nextOrder": 7
            },
            {
                "text": "Yes, I did notice that the library door was ajar, which is unusual since the master always keeps it locked.",
                "order": 4,
                "isOption": false
            },
            {
                "text": "I was mostly busy with preparing the guest rooms and ensuring all the dinner arrangements were perfect.",
                "order": 5,
                "isOption": false
            },
            {
                "text": "I can't believe you'd think I was involved. I've been loyal to this household for over 20 years!",
                "order": 6,
                "isOption": false
            },
            {
                "text": "Well, the weather has been lovely lately, hasn't it? Perfect for a garden stroll.",
                "order": 7,
                "isOption": false
            }
        ],
